Package: xyloR
Title: Tools to Prepare Files for GloboXylo
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Patrick", "Fonti", , "patrick.fonti@wsl.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7070-3292"))
Description: Provides tools to standardize and format observation data and associated metadata for upload to the GloboXylo database. The package ensures data compatibility and adherence to required metadata structures.
